* The *mass* fraction of benzene in liquid phase...... : [______] 




* The *mass* fraction of benzene in vapour phase...... : [______] 



END_PGML

WEIGHTED_ANS($ans1->cmp() ,50);

WEIGHTED_ANS($ans3->cmp() ,50);


